                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <h3 class="black-desc">Disrupting the real estate market</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <p>Unlock the potential of blockchain real estate development with OpenLedger’s team.
                                Eliminate existing inefficiencies, improve business processes and benefit from unique
                                opportunities that blockchain can provide the industry.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
